{"tid":1317207,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你涉嫌冒警及嚴重傷害他人身體，我而家要行使《刑事訴訟程序條例》第101條第2項將你拘捕","createTime":"2019-07-14T17:47:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T07:54:19.000Z","uid":23094,"like":126,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f3bc6b76ff5d20250bc445c49c692f5bb591677f","tid":1317207,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:47:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201411/26/P201411260502.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201411%2F26%2FP201411260502.htm&d=ljlrpVqLOnAgFN3Ei6%2BgJ5Aoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=3cc16bb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201411/26/P201411260502.htm</a><br />\n根據2014年11月26日嘅立法會會議，當時嘅律政司司長袁國強講：<br />\n「因此，問題中提及的「公民逮捕權」，只適用於涉及屬「可逮捕的罪行」。根據香港法例第1章《釋義及通則條例》第3條，「可逮捕的罪行」是指由法律規限固定刑罰的罪行，或根據法例對犯罪人士可處<span style=\"color: red;\">超過12個月</span>監禁的罪行，亦包括犯任何這類罪行的企圖。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap228!zh-Hant-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap228%21zh-Hant-HK&d=ljlrpVqLOnAgFN3Ei6%2BgJ5Aoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=c5ce16f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap228!zh-Hant-HK</a><br />\n根據《簡易程序治罪條例》第22條 第1項：<br />\n「任何人藉任何作為或不作為假冒公職人員，或假裝能促致公職人員作出或不作出與其職責有關的任何作為或事情，不論是否意圖取得任何有價值的東西，均可處罰款$1,000或監禁<span style=\"color: red;\">6個月</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap212!zh-Hant-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap212%21zh-Hant-HK&d=ljlrpVqLOnAgFN3Ei6%2BgJ5Aoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=ed66b1d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap212!zh-Hant-HK</a><br />\n根據《侵害人身罪條例》第19條：<br />\n「任何人非法及惡意傷害他人或對他人身體加以嚴重傷害，不論是否使用武器或器具，均屬犯可循公訴程序審訊的罪行，可處監禁<span style=\"color: red;\">3年</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap221!zh-Hant-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap221%21zh-Hant-HK&d=ljlrpVqLOnAgFN3Ei6%2BgJ5Aoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=ef34f344\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap221!zh-Hant-HK</a><br />\n《刑事訴訟程序條例》第101條 第2項：<br />\n「任何人可無需手令而逮捕<span style=\"color: red;\">任何他合理地懷疑犯了可逮捕的罪行的人</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n《刑事訴訟程序條例》第101A條 第1項：<br />\n「任何人於防止罪案時或於進行或協助合法逮捕罪犯或疑犯或非法地不在羈留中的人時，<span style=\"color: red;\">可使用就當時環境而言屬於合理的武力</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做個良好市民<br />\n制服懷疑冒警暴徒<br />\n維持香港治安，你我有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請法律撚指出錯漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5166a7f9ee7227c39020e12ac186530ac98b71d1","tid":1317207,"uid":23094,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:48:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">制伏</span>先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233e57364c1804af442b42df8f51126e2be1a167","tid":1317207,"uid":23094,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:49:57.000Z","msg":"維持香港治安要靠大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff41356642322c55f2de9dd6da9764347f97dc2f","tid":1317207,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d9bb9f761592a6b87be89f3ec9ccc5e5ae5b50f","tid":1317207,"uid":60398,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:51:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日又要佔領輿論，港台商台火力全開</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316677</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n0800-1000 香港電台第一台<br />\n千禧年代 / Phone in 電話: 1872311<br />\n<br />\n1700-1800 香港電台第一台<br />\n自由風自由Phone / Phone in 電話: 1872311<br />\n<br />\n0630-0700, 0715-1000 雷霆881 (陳志雲版)<br />\n0800-1000 